item.doom.armoredbaron_spawn_egg: Armored Baron of Hell Spawn Egg
doom.astroarmor.text: This armor is brimming with the power.
doom.classicarmor.text: The armor of a time long since past.
doom.crimsonarmor.text: You are one with your past and your rage is red hot now.
doom.cultistarmor.text: The armor created by cultists that worshipped the Nether.
doom.demonicarmor.text: Built from the bodies of the fallen Nether spawn around you.
doom.doomarmor.text: The armor fitting a Demon slayer.
doom.doomicornarmor.text: My Little Doom Slayer, Anger is Magic.
doom.makyrarmor.text: The armor crafted from the fallen beings of the Aether.
doom.midnightarmor.text: You are covered in the ashes of the great Icon of Herobrine.
doom.mulletarmor.text: Business in the front, destruction in the back.
doom.nightmarearmor.text: My Little Doom Slayer, Anger is Magic.
doom.painterarmor.text: We don't make mistakes, just happy little accidents full of Demon blood.
doom.phobosarmor.text: Only given those that process the will and might of a true Slayer.
doom.praetorarmor.text: Crafted by the Wretch for the Doom Slayers Conquest of the Nether.
doom.purplearmor.text: My Little Doom Slayer, Anger is Magic.
doom.sentinelarmor.text: From the time of the Night Sentinels.
doom.zombiearmor.text: Even Death can not hold back the Slayer.
doom.santadoomarmor.text: Docks the halls with Demon guts.
doom.darklordarmor.text: You feel you are prepared now, for this...?
doom.inmortal.text: Makes the Player have 100% Resistance for 30 seconds.
doom.invisible.text: Turns the user invisible for 1 minute.
doom.mega.text: Makes the Player have 200% Health and 100% Resistance for 30 seconds.
doom.argent_engery2.text: souls of the Nether and the power
doom.argent_plate.text: A terrible metal meant for crafting
doom.daisy2.text: Grants the Player unlimited Speed 3 when worn.
doom.marauder_axe1.text: You were never one of us. You were
doom.marauder_axe2.text: nothing but a usurper, a false
doom.marauder_axe3.text: idol. My eyes have been opened.
doom.crucible_sword.text: Rip and Tear. Until it is done.
enchantment.doom.leaping_doom.desc: Allows the player to perform mid-air jump, similar to that of Doom 2016/Eternal
doom.achievement.titan_skull.desc: Find a skull of a long dead Titan.
doom.achievement.portal.desc: Didn't even have to blow a hole into the Overworld to find this
doom.achievement.archmakyr_arena.desc: Find the home of the Arch Maykr.
doom.achievement.motherdemon_arena.desc: Find the home of the Mother Demon.
doom.achievement.hell_church.desc: An abandoned church that worshiped the Demons of the Nether.
doom.achievement.gladiator_fight.desc: Best the Gladiator in the coliseum.
doom.achievement.argent.desc: Created by combining the tortured souls of the Nether and the power of the Aether
doom.achievement.argent_plate.desc: Created by combining the power of Argent Energy and the metal of the Overworld
doom.achievement.icon_fight.desc: As it is written in the prophecies of ancient Villager scripture, the Titans - towering elder demons of the infernal age - would return, unearthed from their immortal slumber.
